:{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 qingzu 123.ogg}} '''Qingzu:''' I'm glad to see you've returned in one piece.
::{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 qingzu 124.ogg}} '''Qingzu:''' So, what happened? Did everything go as planned?
::{{A|VO side2 ywmc1 qingzu 125.ogg}} '''Qingzu:''' Don't worry, your operation was a success &mdash; although your identity was ultimately exposed, you gained a wealth of invaluable intelligence. On top of that, you managed to get out without a scratch.
